data.description: Exciting opportunity to live close to Pearl Brewery in a NEW home with Spanish style exterior featuring concrete tile roof & contemporary interior. 4 bedroom, 3.5 bath, 2864 SF open floor plan w/quartz counters throughout, gas cook top w/ built-in oven and microwave, stainless Bosch appliances, custom wood cabinets in all rooms, 12’ ceilings, 18" x 36" tile floors on first floor, large balcony off second floor game room with built in refrigerator, and an oversized two-car garage with 14’ ceilings and built in overhead garage storage.
